TopicTitle: The next announced mod to get into stock ksp

Articles.Content: The mod has already been announced Caelib. It's Fine Print, a contract based mod.

It's Fine Print. Confirmed in the blog post. Great news, I think!

I actually clapped when I read this. Great news. Here's hoping that they add some mission types on top of it as well. Rescuing Kerbal's from other planets would be nice...
